<h2 id="fixing-the-narrative">Fixing the narrative</h2>

<p>At the core of this problem, was communicating how the mental model of an adaptive lesson works, and the impact it has on students. The visuals that explain this are used in everything, from our website and brand to driving the product design. We needed to frame the benefits in a way anyone could understand and be excited by, and after many iterations, settled on using persona extremes of student understanding as our core narrative.</p>

<figure class="image-grid">
  <div class="items">
    <img src="/assets/projects/aelp/graph-1.jpg" />
    <img src="/assets/projects/aelp/graph-2.jpg" />
    <img src="/assets/projects/aelp/graph-3.jpg" />
