<h2 id="using-it-to-anchor-training">Using it to anchor training</h2>

<p>For this new student-centered narrative to hold, it was important for this to become the standard representation both internally for us, and externally for all our users. We now use it across our brand, product and most importantly for new users, in our knowledge base for explaining how the sample projects work.</p>

